üçÄ Whitepaper: PoF Halving Protocol

Emission & Validator Scaling for GoodLuckcoin (GLC)

---

1. Introduction

GoodLuckcoin (GLC) is a cryptocurrency built on the TON blockchain, powered by a unique consensus mechanism called Proof of Fortune (PoF). Unlike traditional models, PoF selects validators through cryptographic randomness, gamified mechanics, and community engagement.

The PoF Halving Protocol introduces a dual-layered evolution:

- üìâ Scheduled reduction in token emission of earning every two years  
- üìà Doubling of the minimum GLC required to participate in PoF validation

This mechanism transforms validation into a journey ‚Äî where scarcity, strategy, and luck converge.

---

2. Objectives

- üìâ Control inflation through gradual emission of earning reduction  
- üìà Increase token value via scarcity and long-term demand  
- üß† Evolve validator status through rising entry thresholds  
- üéÆ Gamify participation with rituals, ranks, and quests

---

3. Halving Schedule & Validator Scaling

Every two years, the following changes occur:

- Emission per win block is halved  
- Minimum GLC required for PoF validation is doubled  
- Validators ascend through ranks, unlocking privileges and NFT evolution

| Phase           | Year     | Emission Rate | PoF Threshold      | Validator Rank         |
|-----------------|----------|----------------|---------------------|-------------------------|
| Genesis         | 2028     | 100%           | 100,000,000 GLC     | üü¢ Novice of Luck        |
| Halving I       | 2030     | 50%            | 200,000,000 GLC     | üîÆ Adept of Fortune      |
| Halving II      | 2032     | 25%            | 400,000,000 GLC     | üî• Guardian of Chance    |
| Halving III     | 2034     | 12.5%          | 800,000,000 GLC     | üåï Master of Talisman    |
| Final Phase     | 2036+    | 0% (PoF-only)  | 1,600,000,000 GLC   | üß¨ Eternal Validator     |

---

4. PoF Dynamics

As the PoF threshold increases:

- üíé Participation becomes more exclusive  
- üßø NFT Talismans gain strategic importance  
- üìà Luck Level influences validator selection odds  
- ü§ù Validator Pools emerge for collective participation

Validators are not just technical nodes ‚Äî they are keepers of digital luck, ascending through ranks as they accumulate GLC and evolve their talismans.

